<h2 id="retention">Retention</h2>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>CREATE RETENTION POLICY <retention_name> ON <database_name> DURATION <duration_time> REPLICATION \<n> [SHARD DURATION \<duration>] [DEFAULT]</duration></n></duration_time></database_name></retention_name></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>ALTER RETENTION POLICY <retention_name> ON <database_name> DURATION <duration_time> REPLICATION \<n> [SHARD DURATION \<duration>] [DEFAULT]</duration></n></duration_time></database_name></retention_name></p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>reference : <a href="https://docs.influxdata.com/influxdb/v1.7/query_language/database_management/#create-retention-policies-with-create-retention-policy">Document</a></p>
